== Remarks ==
*<br/>This function sets the OpenGL attribute '''attr''' to '''value'''. The requested attributes will take effect after creating an OpenGL context. You should use [[SDL_GL_GetAttribute]]() to check the values after creating the context, since the values obtained can differ from the requested ones.

